CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 11, 1958, page 3, reads: "Congratulations! - Dr. William D. McClelland is congratulated by his deputy coroner, Albert Charles, after being sworn in for a fifth term last week as coroner of Allegheny County. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County Coroner Dr. William D. McClelland seated behind desk with papers in office interior with furniture, two lamps, and flowers
